org.jdesktop.swingx.graphics

Class Graphics2DFacade

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Graphics
      • java.awt.Graphics2D
        • org.jdesktop.swingx.graphics.Graphics2DFacade

  • public abstract class Graphics2DFacade
extends Graphics2D
    A simple facade that forwards all graphics calls to a delegate.

    kschaefer
